## 📦 Enums (Start Here - No Dependencies)

### CarType
```python
class CarType(Enum):
    SEDAN = "SEDAN"           # 4-seater, mid-range
    SUV = "SUV"               # 6-7 seater, premium
    HATCHBACK = "HATCHBACK"   # 4-seater, economy
```

### CarStatus
```python
class CarStatus(Enum):
    AVAILABLE = "AVAILABLE"           # Ready to rent
    RENTED = "RENTED"                 # Currently with a customer
    UNDER_MAINTENANCE = "MAINTENANCE" # Being serviced
```

### BookingStatus
```python
class BookingStatus(Enum):
    RESERVED = "RESERVED"     # Booked, not yet picked up
    ACTIVE = "ACTIVE"         # Customer has the car
    COMPLETED = "COMPLETED"   # Car returned successfully
    CANCELLED = "CANCELLED"   # Booking was cancelled
```

### UserStatus
```python
class UserStatus(Enum):
    UNVERIFIED = "UNVERIFIED"  # Can browse, cannot book
    VERIFIED = "VERIFIED"      # Documents checked, can book
    BLOCKED = "BLOCKED"        # Banned from platform
```

