## 👤 Entity: User

### Attributes
| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `user_id` | UUID/String | Unique identifier |
| `name` | String | Full name |
| `email` | String | Email address (unique) |
| `phone` | String | Contact number |
| `password` | String | Hashed password |
| `license_number` | String | Driving license ID |
| `social_id` | String | Aadhaar/SSN for verification |
| `status` | UserStatus | Verified, Unverified, Blocked |

### Key Decisions
- **license_number required:** Can't rent without valid license
- **status determines booking ability:** Only VERIFIED users can book

### Methods
- `is_verified()` → bool
- `verify()` → marks status as VERIFIED

