## 📋 Entity: Booking

### Attributes
| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `booking_id` | UUID/String | Unique identifier |
| `user_id` | String | Who made the booking |
| `car_id` | String | Which car was booked |
| `start_date` | DateTime | Pickup date/time |
| `end_date` | DateTime | Expected return date/time |
| `actual_return_date` | DateTime | When car was actually returned (for late fee) |
| `booking_date` | DateTime | When booking was created |
| `status` | BookingStatus | Reserved, Active, Completed, Cancelled |
| `total_amount` | float | Total cost charged |
| `late_fee` | float | Penalty if returned late (calculated at return) |

### Key Decisions
- **No branch_id:** We get it from Car (same-branch return enforced)
- **actual_return_date:** Needed to calculate late fees
- **late_fee separate:** Makes it clear what was penalty vs base cost

### Methods
- `calculate_total(daily_rate)` → float
- `calculate_late_fee(penalty_per_day)` → float
- `mark_active()`
- `mark_completed(actual_return)`
- `mark_cancelled()`

