## 🏢 Entity: Branch

### Attributes
| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `branch_id` | UUID/String | Unique identifier |
| `name` | String | Branch name (e.g., "Airport Branch") |
| `address` | String | Full address |
| `cars` | List[Car] | Cars available at this branch |

### Key Decisions
- **cars as List:** Branch "owns" cars
- **Methods are in BranchService:** Entity just holds data

### Methods (Minimal - logic in Service)
