## 🛠️ Services (Logic Layer)

### BookingService
**Responsibility:** Orchestrate the booking flow

**Methods:**
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `create_booking(user, car, start, end)` | Validate user, check availability, calculate cost, create booking |
| `cancel_booking(booking_id)` | Cancel if before pickup, update status |
| `complete_booking(booking_id, return_date)` | Mark completed, calculate late fee if any |
| `get_user_bookings(user_id)` | List all bookings for a user |

### SearchService
**Responsibility:** Find available cars

**Methods:**
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `search_cars(branch, start, end, car_type?)` | Find available cars for date range |
| `get_available_cars(branch_id)` | All available cars at a branch |

### PaymentService
**Responsibility:** Handle payments

**Methods:**
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `process_payment(booking, amount)` | Charge the user |
| `process_refund(booking)` | Refund on cancellation |

