## 🏛️ CarRentalSystem (Singleton - Main Facade)

**Responsibility:** Entry point to the system, holds all branches and services

### Attributes
| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| `branches` | Dict[str, Branch] | All branches by ID |
| `users` | Dict[str, User] | All registered users |
| `bookings` | Dict[str, Booking] | All bookings |
| `booking_service` | BookingService | Booking logic handler |
| `search_service` | SearchService | Search logic handler |

### Methods (Facade - delegates to services)
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `register_user(...)` | Create new user |
| `add_branch(...)` | Add new branch |
| `add_car(branch_id, car)` | Add car to branch |
| `search_cars(...)` | Delegate to SearchService |
| `book_car(...)` | Delegate to BookingService |
| `return_car(...)` | Complete booking |
| `cancel_booking(...)` | Cancel booking |

