## 📐 Design Patterns Used

| Pattern | Where | Why |
|---------|-------|-----|
| **Singleton** | CarRentalSystem | Single entry point, manages all state |
| **Strategy** | PricingStrategy (if needed) | Different pricing for different car types |
| **State** | Booking lifecycle | Reserved → Active → Completed/Cancelled |
| **Factory** | Creating Cars | If car creation becomes complex |

