## 🧪 Implementation Order

| Step | What | Why |
|------|------|-----|
| 1 | Enums | No dependencies |
| 2 | User, Car | Simple entities |
| 3 | Branch | Contains Cars |
| 4 | Booking | Depends on User, Car |
| 5 | Services | Orchestrate entities |
| 6 | CarRentalSystem | Ties everything together |

**Think of it as:**
```
Enums → Simple Entities → Complex Entities → Services → Main System
```

